g by screaming , firing off couple of shots in air or shooting straight to the intruder, everying thing comes in defence. Note: an ALARMING warn is usually  helpful. still if the threat exists, stop it by any means.', 0, 1, '119.153.54.30', 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 'on_nl2br', 2016, 50894),
