(46173, 1589, 46023, 'Conceal Carry', 52, '', 1251081955, '[quote=midreestaj]SO WHAT WE SEE HERE IS: that glock recommends not to oil the firepin ...\nalmost all other parts are oiled.. \nouter barrel, locking lugs, slide rails and internals, trigger system etc[/quote]\n\nFiring pin should be taken out of the firing pin block. Firing pin cavity must be cleaned throughly to remove any gunk which may cause the firing pin to get stuck. firing pin should be wiped clean thorougly and then wiped with an oil soaked cloth. make sure no lint is deposioted in the cavity or the pin. reassemble.', 0, 1, '99.253.204.233', 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 'on_nl2br', 2115, 52823),
