(46176, 623, 14442, 'Conceal Carry', 52, '', 1251082835, '[quote=Abbas]\nIn a nutshell, Grain is the measurement of weight of the projectile itself. The heavier it is the more:\n\n1). Expensive \n2). Hitting Power\n3). Accurate ( less wind drift )\n[b]4). Slower\n5). More Stable in flight[/b].[/quote]\n\nNice info Abbas, I have added two more to the list, I hope you don''t mind.\nThese are the reasons which make them more accurate hence preffered choice of all competetion shooters. They also use less amount of charge, just enough to make them reach the target without too much drop, which in return reduces recoil and muzzle flip also. All this helping to get higher accuracy.', 0, 1, '99.253.204.233', 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 'on_nl2br', 880, 52826),
