ends at PG that they should NOT hunt this endangered specie (or they may get hunted by the Sheikh''s guards.... lol) .. and better do a good "GUZARA"  with "SALAJEET" which is not so expensive and can be found easily all over Pakistan ....lolz\n\nPS : I have photos of various other species of Hubara bustard but I''ll have to find them in my PC and upload them to Photo Bucket before I paste them here.', 0, 1, '119.153.68.173', 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 'on_nl2br', 2296, 57607),
