(51352, 1703, 50102, 'MIdreesTaj', 867, '', 1252424949, '[quote=Skeeter60][quote=12gauge]I''m confused, so... I should change my 9mm handgun and get myself a .22 hornet gun/revolver cause its more potent?\n\nRegards.[/quote]\n\nPlease don''t. In a pistol / Revolver even a .22 LR stinger or a .22 Mag will give same velocity as a hornet when fired from handgun barrel length.\nthe 9mm is much ,much more potent.[/quote]\n\nalso as Skeeter60 sb has said, its better to increase the weight of projectile if you cannot attain much higher velocities due to confined platform (like handgunning for SD). Even a slower but heavier than 9mm projectile would do the job more effectively on 2 legged aggressors i.e Homo Sapiens :)', 0, 1, '119.152.84.119', 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 'on_nl2br', 2265, 58376),
