(51923, 1771, 0, 'Gunfire', 994, '', 1252600518, 'Hi everyone...Just thought I''d post these pictures and share my passion with everyone. While everyone is going inland for big game hunting, I''m going offshore for big game fishing!\n\nThese fish are caught off the cost of Karachi at the Continental Shelf...about 70-100 Nautical Miles off shore where waters are 1000 meters deep. \n\n[img]http://i1020.photobucket.com/albums/af322/Sunseeker44/GiantTrevally.jpg[/img]\nGiant Trevally weighing 52.5 kg.  Took about 45 minutes to reel it in.\n\n\n[img]http://i1020.photobucket.com/albums/af322/Sunseeker44/Marlin.jpg[/img]\nMarlin weighing 295 kg and measuring 110 inches.  Took about 1 hr 50 minutes to reel it in.\n\n\n[img]http://i1020.photobucket.com/albums/af322/Sunseeker44/YellowFinTuna.jpg[/img]\nYellow Fin Tuna weighing 55 kg. Took about 1 hr to reel it in.\n\n\n[img]http://i1020.photobucket.com/albums/af322/Sunseeker44/Sunrise.jpg[/img]\nBeautiful & peaceful sunrise...almost 80 miles offshore. Nothing around you but water & cool breeze! Sometime a bit scary!', 0, 1, '58.181.103.176', 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 'on_nl2br', 2360, 59006),
